descriptionHtml:
Fantasy ENB preset for the latest ENB binary.Live Picture and good performance.
Installation :
Download latest [url=http://enbdev.com/mod_tesskyrim_v0279.htm]ENB[/url] 
-Unzip it.Inside you will find two folders :WrapperVersion and InjectorVersion 
-Copy only "d3d9.dll" , "enbhost.exe" from WrapperVersion folder into your Skyrim root directory 
-Download my mod 
-Extract it 
-Select all files 
-Copy selected files into you Skyrim root directory 
For Better visuals I recommend to download  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/17802/?tab=2&navtag=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fajax%2Fmodfiles%2F%3Fid%3D17802&pUp=1]Climates Of Tamriel - Weather - Lighting - Audio
